    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "### Describe your issue\n\n`TestInline` is amongst the slowest tests in our test suite. We should investigate if that's a general problem with the implementation or just an effect of running each test only once (without caching help), and see if there are ways to speed up either the implementation or at least the test runs.",
    "closed_at": "2026-02-25T08:26:55Z",
